This workshop needs more type theorists:

https://twitter.com/TaliaRinger/status/1409302822940598272

Interested in a machine learning and type theory workshop? Please fill this form out so that I can gauge interest and collect ideas! https://forms.gle/oWUgW67CCChZfs6j8

- Talia Ringer (@TaliaRinger)

https://twitter.com/TaliaRinger/status/1409325879235211268

We have about 30 responses so far, but only 3 who are very experienced or experts in type theory, in contrast with 18 who are very experienced or experts in machine learning. Hopefully my email to types-announce@ helps

- Talia Ringer (@TaliaRinger)
